translations.The status report informs you monthly by: The status report informs you monthly by email about storage space, your shares and gives you useful tips about the MagentaCLOUD.
translations.The activity report informs you every mo: The activity report informs you every morning about all processes in your MagentaCLOUD.
translations.You can use the following list to determ: You can use the following list to determine which activities you would like to be notified of and how often. You can be notified by email or push notification.
